recipeIngredient: 2 scoops vanilla ice cream, chilled (or custard, to serve)

recipeInstructions.text: Combine apple with sultanas, brown sugar and cinnamon in a bowl.
Preheat an electric toasted jaffle maker.
Cut the pastry sheet in half. Lay one half of the pastry across the 2 indents. Top with apple filling and cover with the other half sheet of pastry.
Close jaffle maker, but donâ€™t clip shut. Cook for 23 mins until golden and pastry is crisp. Serve with ice cream.
